<template>
    <svg width="150" height="120" viewBox="0 0 120 80" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="empty-pictorialbar-svg">
    <defs>
        <linearGradient id="pict-bar-grad1" x1="0" y1="1" x2="0" y2="0">
        <stop offset="0%" stop-color="#4F8EF7" stop-opacity="0.7"/>
        <stop offset="100%" stop-color="#A0C4FF" stop-opacity="1"/>
        </linearGradient>
        <linearGradient id="pict-bar-grad2" x1="0" y1="1" x2="0" y2="0">
        <stop offset="0%" stop-color="#FFB300" stop-opacity="0.7"/>
        <stop offset="100%" stop-color="#4F8EF7" stop-opacity="1"/>
        </linearGradient>
        <linearGradient id="pict-bar-grad3" x1="0" y1="1" x2="0" y2="0">
        <stop offset="0%" stop-color="#A0C4FF" stop-opacity="0.7"/>
        <stop offset="100%" stop-color="#FFB300" stop-opacity="1"/>
        </linearGradient>
        <linearGradient id="pict-bar-grad4" x1="0" y1="1" x2="0" y2="0">
        <stop offset="0%" stop-color="#4F8EF7" stop-opacity="0.7"/>
        <stop offset="100%" stop-color="#FFB300" stop-opacity="1"/>
        </linearGradient>
        <linearGradient id="pict-bar-grad5" x1="0" y1="1" x2="0" y2="0">
        <stop offset="0%" stop-color="#FFB300" stop-opacity="0.7"/>
        <stop offset="100%" stop-color="#A0C4FF" stop-opacity="1"/>
        </linearGradient>
    </defs>
    <svg width="0" height="0">
        <defs>
            <linearGradient id="pict-bar-grad1" x1="0" y1="1" x2="0" y2="0">
            <stop offset="0%" stop-color="#4F8EF7" stop-opacity="0.7"/>
            <stop offset="100%" stop-color="#A0C4FF" stop-opacity="1"/>
            </linearGradient>
            <linearGradient id="pict-bar-grad2" x1="0" y1="1" x2="0" y2="0">
            <stop offset="0%" stop-color="#FFB300" stop-opacity="0.7"/>
            <stop offset="100%" stop-color="#4F8EF7" stop-opacity="1"/>
            </linearGradient>
            <linearGradient id="pict-bar-grad3" x1="0" y1="1" x2="0" y2="0">
            <stop offset="0%" stop-color="#A0C4FF" stop-opacity="0.7"/>
            <stop offset="100%" stop-color="#FFB300" stop-opacity="1"/>
            </linearGradient>
            <linearGradient id="pict-bar-grad4" x1="0" y1="1" x2="0" y2="0">
            <stop offset="0%" stop-color="#4F8EF7" stop-opacity="0.7"/>
            <stop offset="100%" stop-color="#FFB300" stop-opacity="1"/>
            </linearGradient>
            <linearGradient id="pict-bar-grad5" x1="0" y1="1" x2="0" y2="0">
            <stop offset="0%" stop-color="#FFB300" stop-opacity="0.7"/>
            <stop offset="100%" stop-color="#A0C4FF" stop-opacity="1"/>
            </linearGradient>
        </defs>
    </svg>
    <g>
        <!-- 象形柱：水滴、星星、圆、矩形、三角依次堆叠 -->
        <g class="pict-bar bar1">
        <!-- 水滴 -->
        <path d="M35 70 Q32 62 35 58 Q38 62 35 70 Z" class="pict-shape drop" />
        </g>
        <g class="pict-bar bar2">
        <!-- 星星 -->
        <polygon points="35,56 37,61 42,61 38,64 39,69 35,66 31,69 32,64 28,61 33,61" class="pict-shape star" />
        </g>
        <g class="pict-bar bar3">
        <!-- 圆 -->
        <circle cx="35" cy="52" r="6" class="pict-shape circle" />
        </g>
        <g class="pict-bar bar4">
        <!-- 矩形 -->
        <rect x="29" y="42" width="12" height="8" rx="3" class="pict-shape rect" />
        </g>
        <g class="pict-bar bar5">
        <!-- 三角 -->
        <polygon points="35,38 41,46 29,46" class="pict-shape triangle" />
        </g>
    </g>
    </svg>
</template>
<script setup>
</script>
<style scoped>
.empty-pictorialbar-svg { display: block; margin: 0 auto; animation: floatX 4.2s ease-in-out infinite; }
.pict-bar .pict-shape {
  opacity: 0.18;
  transform: scaleY(0.2);
  transform-origin: bottom center;
  animation: pict-bar-grow 2.75s cubic-bezier(.4,1.6,.6,1) infinite;
}
.bar1 .drop {
  fill: url(#pict-bar-grad1);
  animation-delay: 0.1s;
}
.bar2 .star {
  fill: url(#pict-bar-grad2);
  animation-delay: 0.35s;
}
.bar3 .circle {
  fill: url(#pict-bar-grad3);
  animation-delay: 0.6s;
}
.bar4 .rect {
  fill: url(#pict-bar-grad4);
  animation-delay: 0.85s;
}
.bar5 .triangle {
  fill: url(#pict-bar-grad5);
  animation-delay: 1.1s;
}
@keyframes pict-bar-grow {
  0% { transform: scaleY(0.2); opacity: 0.12; }
  18% { transform: scaleY(1); opacity: 0.7; }
  80% { transform: scaleY(1); opacity: 0.7; }
  100% { transform: scaleY(0.2); opacity: 0.12; }
}
@keyframes floatX {
    0% { transform: translateY(0) translateX(0); }
    25% { transform: translateY(-8px) translateX(4px); }
    50% { transform: translateY(-12px) translateX(-4px); }
    75% { transform: translateY(-8px) translateX(4px); }
    100% { transform: translateY(0) translateX(0); }
}
</style>
